profile:
ProHanging prides itself as being a high quality option for any household hanging service. Understanding the need to create a unique space means paying attention to detail and listening to the homeowner. Since 2006, ProHanging has been hanging Art, Mirrors, Picture Frames, TV's (TV installations), Blinds, and Specialty items in homes, condos and various institutions throughout the GTA.

You don't pay unless you are 100% satisfied with our service. That's a promise!

Art and Picture hanging is our specialty. We started our organization based on these services and continue to provide a top-notch customer satisfaction service at its finest terms.

We do not provide Electrical work.

Services Include: 

Mounting Service 
*Hanging artwork and sentimental pieces is more than just hammering a nail on the wall, it’s an Art on its own. We inspect all artwork to be safely hung on a particular wall, making sure that artwork will last a lifetime. 
*Mirrors Hanging and Installations 
*Decorative Items Installations
*Window Coverings 
*Blinds Hanging
*Bathroom Accessories Hanging
*Flat Screen TVs Mounting

Give us a call for a quote today and get it installed the right way.

Creative Interiors is a Toronto based design firm, specializing in custom decorating for residential & commercial clients.

Roz Pages’ background derives from the UK, once based in London, one of the top cities in the world for design. Having spent many working holidays in Europe, France & Italy being her favorite, she brings to Toronto a European flair which comes from her passion for fabrics & color. She is dedicated to creating exceptional, distinctive & uniquely personal Interiors.

Roz works with Realtors and has just staged a 5 Million Dollar house located by the Cricket Club. 

Services include:  Interior Decorating, Staging, Project Management and Colour Consultation.
All hired contractors are licensed and insured.

Hi, My name is Barbara. I'm thrilled to announce that I'm celebrating 18 years of Decorating & Designing.

Barbara Nyke Interiors & Design is a residential interior design & decorating studio.  We design custom kitchens, baths and décor for busy professionals primarily in: Toronto, North York, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Caledon, Vaughan, Richmond Hill, The Beach and Scarborough.  For projects located elsewhere, we are delighted to take our designs beyond the GTA.

Here's an article about "Why You Need to Hire a Kitchen Designer" - I'm the featured kitchen designer in the article.. Please copy & paste: https://blog.homestars.com/expert-opinion-why-need-kitchen-designer/

To get your project started, book a 2-hr kitchen design consultation with me.  I'll give you a comprehensive set of preliminary design recommendations including space planning, how to maximize counter space, cabinetry design, estimated project costs and more. Then we're ready for Step 2 of the NIKKA DESIGN process.

--------------

Barbara was a guest designer on "The Property Brothers" TV show.
 
I helped to redesign and renovate the entire main floor of a suburban 1960s home that included: the foyer, dining room, living room, kitchen and family room. Please see our Gallery for some photos.
 
"We design exceptional spaces. Our desire is to serve our valued and respected clientele by transforming how you live and work.  We rely on experience, expertise and impeccable integrity to complete projects on time, on budget and with stunning results".

profile:
What is your time worth to you?  You probably already know that choosing paint colours, fabrics, tiles, home décor, etc. can be a daunting task and become overwhelming.  We pride ourselves on taking care of all the details so you don't have to!  We specialize in renovations, custom design and decorating, colour consultations and preparing your home to sell.  We provide services to fit every home and budget!

Anne Sluman is the owner and lead designer of Refined Staging & Interiors. Anne's love of design, decorating, colour and her attention to detail make her a valuable asset to any home staging or design project.

Anne actually left the industry for many years, for several different reasons and ended up getting into accounting.  Talk about going in a different direction!  Anne worked for a global hearing aid manufacturer for 10 years and continued to work part-time helping client's with their decorating and staging projects, but didn't make it a priority.  A few years ago she and her husband thought about moving. It was during the process of seeing houses with their realtor that Anne's interest and passion for design, decorating and home staging was reignited!

Anne knew in her gut that it was time to return to the business, or would regret it for the rest of her life.  ​Anne quit her job and Refined Staging & Interiors was born.  Anne is so excited and motivated to help her clients love their home or sell their house for top dollar!

Serving Mississauga, Oakville, Burlington, Milton, Halton Hills, Caledon, Georgetown, Brampton, Toronto and surrounding areas.

At S&A Decor we are passionate about design. We believe your home should inspire you, provide comfort and enrich your daily experience of living. We focus on creating fresh lifestyle-based designs infused with comfort and understated luxury. 

The firm imparts a bold, uncluttered design scheme to interiors which hold a timeless grace and elegance. We want you to enjoy the experience as much as you love the design. While each project is unique, our approach to design remains the same - to make each and every space the best it can be, and to ensure that it will stand the test of time
 
S&A Decor is a decorating company specializing in residential interiors. Services include design consultation, space planning, budgeting, purchasing, and project management. Our clients benefit from the impeccable sense of style and professionalism.
